# Override the global gitignore (~/.gitignore_global ignores CLAUDE.md).
# In this repo, CLAUDE.md files are shareable content, so track them.
!CLAUDE.md

# Override the global ignore of .trunk/ so the shared config is tracked.
# .trunk/.gitignore still excludes the local cache/symlinks (out, logs,
# plugins, tools, actions, notifications, user.yaml).
!.trunk/
